egers]]\n|''Harvest'' (''Nature'')\n|[[File:Albert Jaegers - La R\u00e9colte.jpg|100px]]\n|rowspan=\"3\" |1915\n|colspan=\"1\" style=\"background:#87CEEB\" |atop Half-Dome,<br>Court of the Four Seasons,<br>Panama-Pacific International Exposition\n|rowspan=\"3\" |staff\n|\n|rowspan=\"2\" |Jaegers was awarded a PPIE bronze medal for his sculpture.<ref name=\"PPIE Cat\"/>{{rp|237}}<br><br>[[File:Neuhaus Art of Expo p.11.jpg|100px|right]]Half Dome, Court of the Four Seasons:\n|-\n|''Sunshine''<br>''Rain''\n|[[File:Jaegers Sunshine sculpturemuralp00pana 0046.jpg|60px]]<br>[[File:Jaegers Rain sculpturemuralp00pana 0046.jpg|60px]]\n|colspan=\"1\" style=\"background:#87CEEB\" |atop columns flanking the Half-Dome,<br>Court of the Four Seasons,<br>Panama-Pacific International Exposition\n|\n|-\n|''The Feast of Sacrifice''<ref>\"Miss Audrey Monson, and Statues of Her,\" ''The Guthrie Daily Leader'' (Oklahoma), March 20, 1915, p. 1.[https://chroniclingamerica.loc.gov/lccn/sn86063952/1915-03-20/ed-1/seq-1/#date1=1789&sort=relevance&rows=20&words=AUDREY+MUNSON&searchType=basic&sequence=0&index=7&state=&date2=1963&proxtext=Audrey+Munson&y=9&x=12&dateFilterType=yearRange&page=15]</ref>\n|[[File:Jaegers Feast James p.100.jpg|100px]]<br>[[File:Perry Sacrifice sculpturemuralso00panarich 0040.jpg|100px]]\n|colspan=\"1\" style=\"background:#87CEEB\" |Heroic-sized group, repeated twice<br>atop pylons above Forecourt of Ceres,<br>Court of the Four Seasons,<br>Panama-Pacific International Exposition\n|\n|[[File:Court of 4 Seasons Todd Story of Expo vol.1 opp. p.242.jpg|100px|right]]''The Feast of Sacrifice'' (at upper corners):\n|-\n|Augustus Jaegers<ref name=\"Teall\"/>{{rp|435}}\n|''Abundance''<ref>Stella G. S. Perry, ''The Sculpture & Murals of the Panama-Pacific International Exposition'' (San Francisco: The Wahlgreen Company, 1915), p. 33.</ref><br>Attic figures\n|[[File:Jaegers Court of 4 Seasons figure Burness.jpg|60px]]\n|1915\n|colspan=\"1\" style=\"background:#87CEEB\" |Court of 