 for a Head], from SIRIS.</ref>\n|-\n|''Memory''<ref>[https://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?session=1548822816HCA.11078&profile=ariall&source=~!siartinventories&view=subscriptionsummary&uri=full=3100001~!16879~!1&ri=1&aspect=Keyword&menu=search&ipp=20&spp=20&staffonly=&term=French,+Daniel+Chester+&index=.AW&uindex=&oper=&term=Memory&index=.TW&uindex=&aspect=Keyword&menu=search&ri=1 Memory], from SIRIS.</ref>\n|[[File:Memory by Daniel Chester French 02.jpg|100px]]\n|modeled<br>{{circa}}1909<br><br>carved<br>1917\u20131919\n|[[Metropolitan Museum of Art]],<br>Manhattan, New York City\n|marble\n|{{cvt|57.5|in|cm|sortable=on}}\n|[[File:Chesterwood (Stockbridge, MA) - studio interior.JPG|100px|right]]A plaster model is at [[Chesterwood (Massachusetts)|Chesterwood]], French's home<br>and studio in Stockbridge, Massachusetts.<br>(Pictured, center)<br><br>\n|-\n|''Jurisprudence''<ref>[https://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?session=1O4H8555U7741.35&menu=search&aspect=Keyword&npp=50&ipp=20&spp=20&profile=ariall&ri=&term=Jurisprudence&index=.GW&aspect=Keyword&term=French%2C+Daniel+Chester&index=.AW&term=&index=.TW&term=&index=.SW&term=&index=.FW&term=&index=.OW&term=&index=.NW&x=9&y=16 Jurisprudence], from SIRIS.</ref>\n|[[File:Jurisprudence by Daniel Chester French, 1912 - Cleveland, Ohio - DSC07960.JPG|100px]]\n|1910\u20131912\n|rowspan=\"2\" |[[Howard M. Metzenbaum United States Courthouse|Metzenbaum United States Courthouse]],<br>Cleveland, Ohio\n|marble\n|{{cvt|12|ft|m|sortable=on}}\n|rowspan=\"2\" |[[File:Southwest fa\u00e7ade, Howard M. Metzenbaum U.S. Courthouse, Cleveland, Ohio LCCN2010719498.tif|100px|right]]Located at street level, near the corners of the<br>Superior Avenue fa\u00e7ade.\n|-\n|''Commerce''<ref>[https://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?session=1548H5E667D49.46&menu=search&aspect=Keyword&npp=50&ipp=20&spp=20&profile=ariall&ri=&term=&index=.GW&aspect=Keyword&term=French&index=.AW&term=Commerce&index=.TW&term=&index=.SW&term=&index=.FW&term=&index=.OW&term=&index=.NW&x=16&y=10 Commerce], from SIRIS.</ref>\n|[[File:Commerce by Daniel Chester French, 1912 - Cleveland, Ohio - DSC07914.JPG|100px]]\n|1910\u20131912\n|marble\n|{{cvt|12|ft|m|sortable=on}}\n|-\n|''[[Wisconsin (statue)|Wisconsin'' (''Forward'')]]<ref>[https://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?session=J5L882055P075.10967&menu=search&aspect=Keyword&npp=50&ipp=20&spp=20&profile=ariall&ri=&term=&index=.GW&aspect=Keyword&term=French%2C+Daniel+Chester&index=.AW&term=Wisconsin&index=.TW&term=&index=.SW&term=&index=.FW&term=&index=.OW&term=&index=.NW&x=7&y=15 Forward], from SIRIS.</ref>\n|[[File:Statue atop the Wisconsin State Capitol Building titled \"Wisconsin\".jpg|100px]]\n|1912\n|[[Wisconsin State Capitol]],<br>Madison, Wisconsin\n|gilded bronze\n|{{cvt|15.5|ft|m|sortable=on}}\n|[[File:Wisconsin State Capitol dome - Madison, WI - DSC02746.JPG|100px|right]]Atop Wisconsin State Capitol Dome:\n|-\n|colspan=\"1\" style=\"background:#FFDEAD\" |''Evangeline''<ref name=\"Munson Chapter 3\">Audrey Munson, \"By the 'Queen of the Artists' Studios,' Chapter 3.\" ''The Pittsburgh Press'', January 23, 1921, p. 79.</ref><ref>[https://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?session=15E8U217631Q7.11034&profile=ariall&source=~!siartinventories&view=subscriptionsummary&uri=full=3100001~!335798~!3&ri=1&aspect=Keyword&menu=search&ipp=20&spp=20&staffonly=&term=Longfellow&index=.GW&uindex=&oper=&term=French,+Daniel+Chester&index=.AW&uindex=&aspect=Keyword&menu=search&ri=1 Longfellow Monument], from SIRIS.</ref><br>(bas relief figure, 2nd from right)\n|[[File:DCF Longfellow SAAM-J0108331.jpg|100px]]\n|1912\u20131914\n|Henry Wadsworth Longfellow Memorial,<br>Longfellow Park,<br>Cambridge, Massachusetts\n|marble\n|{{cvt|36|in|cm|sortable=on}}\n|[[File:Henry Wadsworth Longfellow Memorial by Daniel Chester French.JPG|100px|right]]In Longfellow Park:\n|-\n|''[[The Spirit of Life]]''<ref>[https://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.j